## Step 3 — Extract Brand Tokens

Scan for CSS custom properties at `:root` level, or repeated hex values.

```css
/* From HTML :root */
:root {
  --bg: #f8f9fa;
  --surface: #ffffff;
  --sidebar: #0e1029;
  --accent: #9db8ee;
  --success: #329547;
  --error: #ec6369;
  --warning: #ffb704;
  --text: #112431;
  --muted: #6b7280;
  --border: #d9dfe3;
}
```

Map to `const T` inline in your composition file:

```ts
const T = {
  navy:    "#0E1029",   // background (override with HTML's --sidebar or --bg-dark)
  mist:    "#9DB8EE",   // accent
  bg:      "#f8f9fa",   // light mode background
  surface: "#ffffff",   // card surface
  text:    "#112431",   // primary text
  muted:   "#6b7280",
  light:   "#a4afb7",
  border:  "#d9dfe3",
  success: "#329547",
  error:   "#ec6369",
  warning: "#ffb704",
  info:    "#0066cc",
  font:    "'Inter', sans-serif",
};
```

